%20of%20Staff%20Joseph%20Dunford%20is%20welcomed%20by%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%2C%20chief%20of%20the%20general%20staff%20of%20the%20Chinese%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20Gen.%20Fang%20Fenghui%3Cp%3EThomas%20Peter%2FPool%20Photo%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20on%20a%202020%20hack%20on%20the%20Japanese%20military%20conducted%20by%20Chinese%20cyberspies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20hack%20gave%20Chinese%20spies%20access%20to%20Japanese%20military%20plans%2C%20capabilities%2C%20and%20shortcomings.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChina%20has%20been%20escalating%20its%20cyberattacks%20on%20foreign%20militaries%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20including%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20escalating%20cyber%20attacks%20aren't%20limited%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-officials-found-chinese-malware-hidden-in-military-systems-2023-7%5C%22%3Emalware%20discovered%20in%20US%20military%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20new%20reporting%20from%20The%20Washington%20Post%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Post%20on%20Monday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2023%2F08%2F07%2Fchina-japan-hack-pentagon%2F%5C%22%3Edetailed%20a%20previously%20unreported%20hack%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20Japanese%20military%20networks%20by%20China's%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20in%202020.%20The%20hack%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-spy-agencies-five-poisons-taiwan-tibet-uighur-democracy-2023-8%5C%22%3EChinese%20cyberspies%3C%2Fa%3E%20access%20to%20Japanese%20military%20plans%2C%20capabilities%2C%20and%20shortcomings%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20bad%20%E2%80%94%20shockingly%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20U.S.%20military%20official%2C%20who%20was%20briefed%20on%20the%20event%2C%20told%20the%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20is%2C%20strategically%2C%20the%20United%20States'%20most%20important%20ally%20in%20East%20Asia.%20The%20news%2C%20coupled%20with%20reports%20from%20May%20of%20China%20installing%20malware%20into%20US%20military%20systems%2C%20signals%20a%20significant%20escalation%20in%20how%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20%E2%80%94%20the%20military%20arm%20of%20China's%20ruling%20communist%20party%20%E2%80%94%20is%20targeting%C2%A0foreign%20adversaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202020%20hack%20was%20among%20the%20most%20damaging%20in%20Japan's%20recent%20history%2C%20with%20Chinese%20intelligence%20maintaining%20deep%20and%20pervasive%20access%20to%20Japanese%20networks%20into%20early%202021%2C%20the%20Post%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Insider%20previously%20reported%2C%20US%20officials%20indicated%20that%20investigations%20into%20Chinese%20malware%20had%20been%20underway%20for%20several%20months%20after%20discovering%20that%20malicious%20code%20had%20infiltrated%20US%20military%20systems%20across%20the%20country%20and%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrevious%20cyber%20attacks%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-hackers-are-tearing-the-navy-and-its-industry-partners-apart-2019-3%5C%22%3Efocused%20on%20surveillance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rather%20than%20disruption%20of%20system%20processes%2C%20but%20the%20latest%20attacks%20appear%20targeted%20to%20throw%20US%20military%20and%20civilian%20operations%20into%20disarray%2C%20according%20to%20military%20and%20intelligence%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20years%20we%20have%20been%20concerned%20about%20its%20espionage%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20U.S.%20official%20told%20the%20Post.%20%26quot%3BBut%20China%20is%20%5Balso%5D%20developing%20cyberattack%20capabilities%20that%20could%20be%20used%20to%20di