s%2Fbecause-they-lost-4-elections-to-aap-arvind-kejriwal-after-delhi-bill-clears-parliament-4277910%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Amit%20Shah's%20Fraud%20Claim%20Against%20AAP%20Motion%2C%20Raghav%20Chadha%20Said...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20alleged%20fraud%20in%20a%20motion%20moved%20by%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Raghav%20Chadha%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill.%20Responding%20to%20the%20debate%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20before%20the%20bill%20was%20voted%20on%20this%20evening%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20the%20motion%20has%20the%20names%20of%20five%20MPs%20that%20were%20included%20fraudulently%20and%20the%20matter%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated%20by%20parliament's%20Privilege%20Committee.%20Mr%20Chadha%20sidestepped%20the%20issue%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20respond%20if%20the%20Privilege%20Committee%20sends%20him%20a%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20motion%20to%20send%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill%20to%20Select%20Committee%20was%20moved%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20MP%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20MPs%20are%20now%20claiming%20that%20they%20did%20not%20second%20it.%20Sasmit%20Patra%20of%20the%20BJD%20said%20he%20never%20gave%20consent%20for%20inclusion%20in%20the%20motion.%20How%20could%20his%20name%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20triggering%20chaos%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Opposition%20members%20were%20on%20their%20feet%20shouting%20in%20protest%2C%20the%20minister%2C%20who%20introduced%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20bill%20in%20the%20house%2C%20said%20this%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20privilege%20and%20should%20be%20investigated%20by%20the%20privilege%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFour%20members%20have%20sent%20a%20complaint%20to%20me.%20It%20will%20be%20inquired%20into%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Deputy%20chairman%20Harivansh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MPs%20are%20Narhani%20Amin%2C%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi