gov.uscourts.ca5.214615%2Fgov.uscourts.ca5.214615.42.1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblocked%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Education%20Department's%20new%20rules%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%20who%20said%20they%20were%20defrauded%20by%20the%20school%20they%20attended%20to%20get%20their%20debt%20wiped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20Career%20Colleges%20and%20Schools%20of%20Texas%2C%20a%20for-profit%20college%20group%2C%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20Education%20Department%20to%20block%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-just-got-easier-defrauded-borrowers-debt-relief-2023-2%5C%22%3Eits%20latest%20changes%20to%20the%20borrower%20defense%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allow%20a%20borrower%20who%20proved%20they%20were%20defrauded%20to%20have%20their%20loans%20discharged.%20The%20rules%20would%20create%20a%20more%20streamlined%20application%20process%20for%20borrowers%20seeking%20debt%20relief%2C%20along%20with%20expanding%20the%20types%20of%20misconduct%20that%20would%20qualify%20a%20borrower%20for%20a%20loan%20discharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECCST%20argued%20in%20its%20original%20complaint%20that%20the%20department%20stacked%20%26quot%3Bthe%20deck%20in%20favor%20of%20borrowers%20and%20against%20schools%3B%20the%20Rule%20imposes%20strict%20liability%20upon%20schools%20for%20even%20unintentional%20erroneous%20representations%20or%20omissions%2C%20and%20then%20irrationally%20presumes%20that%20every%20borrower%20in%20the%20group%20would%20not%20have%20attended%20the%20school%20but%20for%20the%20school's%20act%20or%20omission%2C%20whatever%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20district%20court%20rejected%20the%20group's%20request%20for%20an%20emergency%20injunction%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20the%20Fifth%20Circuit%20obliged%20%E2%80%94%20blocking%20the%20new%20rule%20from%20being%20carried%20out%20for%20the%20time%20being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20and%20CCST%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20Aaron%20Ament%2C%20president%20of%20borrower%20protection%20group%20Student%20Defense%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20cannot%20afford%20a%20green%20light%20for%20dishonest%20schools%20to%20continue%20harming%20students.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefrauded%20borrowers%20are%20legally%20entitled%20to%20relief%20and%20their%20institutions%20should%20be%20held%20accountable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BUntil%20these%20protections%20are%20restored%2C%20countless%20students%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20taken%20advantage%20of%20by%20higher%20ed%20profiteers%20who%20are%20exploiting%20students%20with%20little%20accountability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20said%20in%20a%20July%20legal%20filing%20that%20%26quot%3BCCST's%20alleged%20injuries%20are%20entirely%20speculative%20and%2C%20in%20any%20event%2C%20insufficient%20to%20constitute%20irreparable%20injury%20directly%20attributable%20to%20the%20Rule.%20Even%20if%20this%20Court%20concludes%20that%20CCST%20has%20adequately%20established%20some%20irreparable%20injury%2C%20that%20threatened%20injury%20plainly%20could%20not%20outweigh%20the%20damage%20that%20an%20injunction%20would%20cause%20the%20public%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20department's%20new%20rules%20for%20borrower%20defense%20will%20be%20blocked%20as%20the%20legal%20process%20proceeds.%20Jason%20Altmire%2C%20president%20of%20Career%20Education%20Colleges%20and%20Universities%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20that%20represents%20for-profit%20colleges%20%E2%80%94%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bknowing%20that%20this%20rule%20has%20a%20strong%20chance%20to%20be%20struck%20down%20during%20the%20upcoming%20legal%20process%2C%20it%20is%20unjustifiable%20to%20allow%20its%20implementation%20while%20the%20court%20proceedings%20continue.%20We%20are%20pleased%20that%20today's%20ruling%20upholds%20this%20view.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-borrower-defense-rules-fifth-circuit-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691431737000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d12c9720f1cf0019cc3960%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-borrower-defense-rules-fifth-circuit-biden-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Fifth%20Circuit%20ruled%20in%20favor%20of%20a%20for-profit%20college%20group%20to%20block%20Biden's%20new%20borrower%20defense%20rules.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-borrower-defense-rules-fifth-circuit-biden-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GOP%20presidential%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20calls%20Juneteenth%20a%20'useless'%20holiday%202%20months%20after%20he%20said%20the%20holiday%20should%20be%20a%20'celebration%20of%20the%20American%20Dream'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivek%20Ramaswamy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d12dcbf5d4870019e34cf0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERepublican%20presidential%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FCharlie%20Neibergall%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERepublican%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20blasted%20Juneteenth%20while%20speaking%20in%20Iowa%2C%20calling%20the%20holiday%20%26quot%3Buseless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwo%20months%20ago%2C%20he%20praised%20the%20holiday%2C%20saying%20it%20should%20be%20a%20%2