%5C%22%3EEarly%20voting%20featured%20long%20lines%20in%20some%20of%20the%20state's%20largest%20counties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20it%20almost%20guaranteed%20the%20race%20will%20smash%20last%20year's%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20abortion%20is%20legal%20up%20to%2022%20weeks%20of%20pregnancy%2C%20but%20that%20is%20only%20because%20a%20much%20more%20restrictive%20ban%20has%20been%20put%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOhio%20Gov.%20Mike%20DeWine%2C%20a%20Republican%2C%20previously%20signed%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bheartbeat%20bill%26quot%3B%20into%20law%20that%20would%20effectively%20ban%20almost%20all%20abortions%20after%20six%20weeks%20of%20pregnancy.%20The%20law%20did%20not%20include%20exceptions%20for%20rape%20or%20incest.%20An%20Ohio%20judge%20previously%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.wosu.org%2F2023-04-07%2Fohio-governor-says-lawmakers-should-clarify-six-week-abortion-ban-now-on-hold-by-a-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estayed%20the%20law%20pending%20legal%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20amendment%20that%20will%20go%20before%20voters%20in%20November%20would%20establish%20a%20state%20constitutionally-protected%20right%20to%20abortion%20access.%20It%20would%20allow%20restrictions%20after%20fetal%20viability%2C%20which%20is%20around%2024%20weeks%20of%20pregnancy.%20Fetal%20viability%20was%20the%20standard%20established%20by%20Roe%20v.%20Wade%20until%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gutted%20nationwide%20abortion%20rights%20in%20its%202022%20landmark%20ruling%20in%20Dobbs%20v.%20Jackson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERepublicans%20still%20haven't%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20talk%20about%20abortion.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENationally%2C%20conservatives%20are%20still%20grappling%20to%20find%20an%20effective%20response%20on%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20midterms%20illustrated%20that%20voters%20are%20furious%20over%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision.%20The%20GOP%20presidential%20primary%20race%20ha