Wilking%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENvidia%20is%20still%20a%20%26quot%3Btop%20pick%26quot%3B%20stock%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20even%20after%20its%20AI-driven%20year-to-date%20rally%20of%20209%25.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bank%20said%20Nvidia's%20upcoming%202nd-quarter%20earnings%20report%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bless%20shock%20and%20awe%26quot%3B%20and%20more%20about%20execution.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20biggest%20risk%20for%20Nvidia%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20scale%20the%20supply%20of%20its%20AI-enabling%20GPU%20chips%2C%20according%20to%20BofA.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains%20a%20%26quot%3Btop%20sector%20pick%26quot%3B%20ahead%20of%20its%20upcoming%20second-quarter%20earnings%20report%2C%20even%20after%20its%20stunning%20AI-driven%20year-to-date%20stock%20rally%20of%20209%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fbac-stock%5C%22%3EBank%20of%20America's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Vivek%20Arya%2C%20who%20in%20a%20Monday%20note%20reiterated%20his%20%26quot%3BBuy%26quot%3B%20rating%20and%20%24550%20price%20target%20for%20Nvidia%2C%20suggesting%20potential%20upside%20of%2022%25%20from%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Arya%20still%20sees%20a%20rosy%20future%20for%20Nvidia%20as%20it%20helps%20power%20the%20growing%20artificial%20intelligence%20industry%20with%20its%20GPU%20accelerators%2C%20he%20admits%20that%20the%20company%20will%20have%20%26quot%3Bless%20shock%20and%20awe%26quot%3B%20for%20investors%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-ai-race-artificial-intelligence-wall-street-gpu-huang-2023-5%5C%22%3Eit%20issued%20a%20massively%20bullish%20guidance%20update%20in%20May.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Instead%2C%20Arya%20expects%20Nvidia%20to%20transition%20towards%20a%20period%20of%20execution%20that%20will%20be%20defined%20by%20its%20ability%20to%20scale%20supply%20to%20meet%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20the%20sentiment%20to%20be%20%5Ba%5D%20bit%20more%20measured.%20Demand%20isn't%20the%20issue%2C%20its%20supply%20and%20importantly%20the%20pace%20with%20which%20US%20cloud%20service%20providers%20are%20able%20to%20set%20up%20genAI%20compute%20instances%2C%26quot%3B%20Arya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArya%20expects%20Nvidia%20to%20report%20second-quarter%20revenue%20of%20at%20or%20slightly%20above%20%2411%20billion%2C%20which%20would%20represent%20year-over-year%20revenue%20growth%20of%2064%25.%20Arya%20said%20he%20also%20expects%20Nvidia's%20third-quarter%20revenue%20to%20accelerate%20up%20to%20100%25%20to%20about%20%2412%20billion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20perhaps%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20near-term%20direction%20of%20Nvidia's%20stock%20price%20hinges%20on%20guidance%20comments%20from%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20and%20as%20to%20whether%20these%20revenue%20gains%20are%20a%20short-term%20blip%20or%20have%20staying%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20will%20look%20for%20clues%20on%20sustainability%20of%20these%20elevated%20forecasts%20considering%20a%20lukewarm%20US%20cloud%20service%20provider%20capex%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Arya%20said.%20%26quot%3BListen%20for%20management%20commentary%20around%20continued%20sales%20acceleration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20post-earnings%20reaction%20to%20Nvidia's%20upcoming%20earnings%20report%20could%20ultimately%20see%20some%20%26quot%3Bnear-term%20stock%20consolidation%26quot%3B%20after%20its%20solid%20year-to-date%20rally.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20expect%20Nvidia%20stock%20to%20trade%20sideways%20or%20slightly%20lower%20after%20it%20reports%20earnings%20after%20the%20market%20close%20on%20August%2023%2C%20according%20to%20Arya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-artificial-intelligence-nvidia-chip-revenues-stock-price-jensen-huang-2023-7%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20long-term%20opportunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20what%20Arya%20is%20focused%20on.%20The%20analyst%20estimated%20that%20Nvidia%20could%20%26quot%3Bmarch%20towards%26quot%3B%20%2420%20to%20%2425%20in%20long-term%20earnings%20per%20share%2C%20which%20would%20help%20make%20its%20current%20forward%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%20of%2039x%20more%20digestible%20for%20investors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20forecast%20AI%20servers%20to%20grow%20at%20a%2037%25%20compounded%20annual%20growth%20rate%20from%201.23%20million%20in%202023%20(8%25%20to%2010%25%20of%20all%20servers)%20towards%204.4%20million%20by%202027%20(%2B25%25%20of%20all%20servers)%2C%20enabling%20Nvidia's%20total%20sales%20to%20expand%20at%20a%2026%25%20CAGR%20to%20%24109%20billion%2C%26quot%3B%20Arya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20BofA%20isn't%20the%20only%20Wall%20Street%20bank%20with%20a%20%24100%2B%20billion%20revenue%20projection%20for%20Nvidia%20by%202027.%20Mizuho%20said%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-artificial-intelligence-nvidia-chip-revenues-stock-price-jensen-huang-2023-7%5C%22%3Ecould%20generate%20more%20than%20%24300%20billion%20in%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202027.%20For%20context%2C%20Nvidia%20generated%20revenue%20of%20about%20%2427%20billion%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20stock%20traded%20up%20just%20over%201%25%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20is%20down%20just%20over%206%25%20from%20its%2052-week%20high%20of%20%24488.88.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-still-top-pick-2q-earnings-ai-rally-bofa-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691428634000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3ebe9442f43f001ddfe197%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2