s%20Rajya%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20passed%20by%20131%20to%20102%20votes.%20Four%20MPs%20have%20abstained.%20The%20Opposition%2C%20which%20put%20up%20a%20strong%20fight%2C%20was%20bested%20by%20the%20joint%20efforts%20of%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20ruling%20YSR%20Congress%20and%20opposition%20TDP%2C%20which%20declared%20support%20for%20the%20government%20last%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpeaking%20against%20the%20bill%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Raghav%20Chadha%20exhorted%20the%20BJP%20to%20follow%20their%20own%20leaders%20--%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20LK%20Advani%20--%20who%20wanted%20full-fledged%20statehood%20for%20Delhi.%20The%20BJP%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20is%20reacting%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20have%20lost%20multiple%20consecutive%20elections%20in%20Delhi.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Chadha%20also%20said%20the%20Delhi%20government%20will%20go%20to%20court%20again%20on%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECongress's%20P%20Chidambaram%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20neither%20constitutional%20nor%20moral%20authority%20to%20pass%20this%20bill.%20%26quot%3BYou%20won%20an%20election%20(in%20Delhi)%2025%20years%20ago%2C%20what%20moral%20right%20do%20you%20have%3F%20The%20bill%20is%20what%20the%20government%20thinks%20is%20a%20model%20for%20Delhi.%20They%20invented%20a%20model%20for%20J%26amp%3BK%20which%20is%20in%20court%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Constitution's%20Article%20370%20that%20bestowed%20special%20status%20on%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20moved%20the%20bill%2C%20said%20the%20Delhi%20services%20bill%20doesn't%20violate%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%2C%20which%20maintained%20that%20the%20elected%20government%20is%20the%20boss%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20bill%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20essentially%20gives%20the%20same%20powers%20to%20the%20Delhi%20government%20that%20were%20there%20during%20the%20Congress%20rule.%20The%20Congress%20is%20now%20opposing%20the%20bill%20%26quot%3Bto%20appease%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party...%20They%20are%20now%20sitting%20in%20AAP's%20lap%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDelhi's%20ruling%20AAP%2C%20which%20would%20be%20most%20affected%20by%20the%20proposed%20law%2C%20has%20been%20campaigning%20against%20it%20for%20weeks%2C%20rallying%20the%20Opposition.%20AAP%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20proposed%20law%20will%20set%20a%20precedent%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20strip%20any%20Opposition-ruled%20state%20of%20its%20power%20of%20governance%2C%20sidelining%20the%20elected%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpeaking%20shortly%20after%20the%20bill%20was%20passed%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20doing%20this%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20the%20work%20we%20did%20in%207-8%20years%20without%20any%20power%2C%20they%20couldn't%20do%20the%20same%20despite%20being%20in%20power%20for%2030%20years%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%A6%20They%20have%20government%20in%20Manipur%2C%20they%20burnt%20down%20Manipur%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Services%20bill%2C%20which%20replaces%20an%20Ordinance%20that%20wrested%20control%20of%20bureaucrats%20from%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20had%20passed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20test%20by%20a%20voice%20vote%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20hiccup%20was%20expected%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20where%20the%20NDA%20is%20yet%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20proposed%20law%20will%20empower%20the%20Central%20Government%20to%20control%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%20by%20having%20the%20final%20say%20in%20the%20postings%2C%20transfers%20of%20bureaucrats%20and%20employees.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691427600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F