%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Contaminants%20Found%20in%20Yet%20Another%20India-Made%20Drug%2C%20WHO%20Issues%20Alert%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07221054%2FIraq-contaminated-medicine.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20has%20issued%20a%20product%20alert%20against%20yet%20another%20Indian%20medicine.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20it%20has%20found%20contaminants%20diethylene%20glycol%20and%20ethylene%20glycol%20in%20a%20syrup%20made%20by%20an%20Indian%20manufacturer%20and%20marketed%20by%20another%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20alert%20issued%20on%20August%207%2C%20the%20UN%20health%20body%20has%20detected%20DEG%20and%20EG%20in%20Cold%20Out%20syrup%20(Paracetamol%20and%20chlorpheniramine%20maleate).%20It%20is%20used%20for%20cold%20and%20flu.%20The%20DEG%20and%20EG%20have%20been%20found%20to%20the%20tune%20of%200.25%25%20and%202.1%25%20respectively.%20Fouurts%20(India)%20Laboratories%20Pvt%20Limited%2C%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20company%2C%20has%20made%20the%20product%20while%20Dabilife%20Pharma%20Pvt%20Ltd%20India%20has%20marketed%20it.%20The%20product%20was%20exported%20to%20Iraq%20and%20samples%20were%20collected%20from%20a%20location%20in%20the%20country%20for%20laboratory%20analysis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETerming%20the%20presence%20of%20contaminants%20unacceptably%20high%2C%20the%20WHO%20said%20both%20DEG%20and%20EG%20are%20not%20permitted%20beyond%200.10%25.%20DEG%20is%20an%20industrial%20solvent%20and%20is%20used%20as%20brake%20fluid.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20substandard%20batch%20of%20the%20product%20referenced%20in%20this%20Alert%20is%20unsafe%20and%20its%20use%2C%20especially%20in%20children%2C%20may%20result%20in%20serious%20injury%20or%20death.%20Toxic%20effects%20can%20include%20abdominal%20pain%2C%20vomiting%2C%20diarrhoea%2C%20inability%20to%20pass%20urine%2C%20headache%2C%20altered%20mental%20state%20and%20acute%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ekidney%20injury%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20death%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20the%20alert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20WHO%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20date%2C%20the%20stated%20manufacturer%20and%20the%20marketer%20have%20not%20provided%20guarantees%20to%20WHO%20on%20the%20safety%20and%20quality%20of%20the%20product.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20alert%20comes%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20several%20other%20alerts%20issued%20against%20drugs%20made%20in%20India.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20biggest%20scandal%20to%20hit%20the%20Indian%20pharma%20industry%20was%20the%20deaths%20of%2070%20children%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F05-10-2022-medical-product-alert-n-6-2022-substandard-(contaminated)-paediatric-medicines%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGambia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Despite%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fgambia-cough-syrup-sue-indian-government%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efour%20detailed%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20besides%20lab%20reports%20of%20WHO%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20refused%20to%20accept%20this%20incident%20as%20that%20of%20DEG%20and%20EG%20poisoning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20the%20WHO%20found%20DEG%20and%20EG%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F19-07-2023-medical-product-alert-n-5-2023--substandard-(contaminated)-syrup-medicines%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENaturcold%20syrup%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20was%20exported%20to%20Cameroon.%20The%20manufacturer%20%E2%80%93%20Fraken%20International%20%E2%80%93%20was%20listed%20on%20the%20product%20carton%20as%20UK-based.%20However%2C%20the%20UK%20drug%20regulator%20confirmed%20to%20the%20WHO%20that%20there%20was%20no%20manufacturer%20by%20that%20name%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%20Later%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20was%20found%20to%20be%20India-based.%20The%20government%20issued%20a%20stop%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhealthcare-pharmaceuticals%2Findia-orders-riemann-labs-linked-cough-syrup-deaths-cameroon-stop-manufacturing-2023-08-01%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20manufacturing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20order%20to%20it%20.%20Six%20children%20died%20in%20this%20posinning%20incident.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20deaths%20of%20seven%20children%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fuzbekistan-child-deaths-three-of-noida-based-firm-arrested-for-contaminated-medicines%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUzbekistan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20linked%20to%20two%20drugs%20made%20in%20India%2C%20again%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20DEG%20and%20EG%20in%20them.%20The%20Indian%20government%20also%20found%20the%20contamination%20in%20its%20own%20investigation.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691426644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07221054%2FIraq-contaminated-medicine.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fcontaminants-found-in-yet-another-india-made-drug-who-issues-alert%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20WHO%2C%20Diethyelene%20glycol%20and%20ethylene%20glycol%20have%20been%20found%20in%20'unacceptable%20amounts'.%20The%20same%20toxins%20were%20found%20earlier%20in%20other%20substandard%20drugs%20exported%20from%20India%20to%20Gambia%2C%20Uzbekistan%2C%20and%20Cameroon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fcontaminants-found-in-yet-another-india-made-drug-who-issues-alert%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uk