20statement%20came%20hours%20after%20he%20moved%20the%20bill%20for%20passage%20in%20the%20House%20after%20opposition%20members%20moved%20a%20resolution%20disapproving%20the%20ordinance%20brought%20by%20the%20government%20in%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20tried%20to%20block%20Mr%20Shah's%20address%20at%20least%20thrice%20for%20allegedly%20using%20unparliamentary%20words%20and%20deviating%20from%20the%20agenda%20of%20debate%20but%20their%20points%20of%20order%20were%20ruled%20out%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20chief%20strategist%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20bill%20was%20first%20brought%20by%20the%20Congress%20when%20it%20was%20in%20power.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20assure%20that%20none%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20bill%20are%20changed%20from%20what%20it%20was%20in%20the%20Congress%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20appeasing%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20by%20%26quot%3Bopposing%20the%20bill%20it%20itself%20brought%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20now%20sitting%20in%20AAP's%20lap%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20amid%20a%20huge%20uproar%20by%20the%20opposition%20in%20parliament%20for%20using%20an%20unparliamentary%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BAAP%20government%20in%20Delhi%20transferred%20officers%20in%20vigilance%20department%20as%20liquor%20scam%20files%20were%20with%20it%26quot%3B%20while%20giving%20a%20%26quot%3Bchronology%20of%20the%20events%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20ruling%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20ordered%20immediate%20transfers%20in%20vigilance%20dept%20as%20it%20was%20probing%20scams%2C%20including%20in%20Chief%20Minister%20house%20renovation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20also%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress%2C%20saying%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20will%20quit%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20once%20the%20Delhi%20services%20bill%20is%20passed.%20Continuing%20his%20tirade%20against%20the%20opposition%20parties%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20opposing%20the%20Delhi%20services%20bill%20only%20to%20save%20their%20alliance%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20won't%20matter%20even%20if%20more%20parties%20join%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20again%20become%20PM%20in%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20a%20point%20of%20order%20was%20raised%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20who%20insisted%20that%20Mr%20Shah%20should%20talk%20about%20the%20bill%20and%20not%20about%202024%20and%20should%20avoid%20resorting%20to%20personal%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20empowers%20the%20Central%20Government%20to%20make%20rules%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%2C%20including%20the%20functions%2C%20terms%2C%20and%20other%20conditions%20of%20service%20of%20officers%20and%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20Centre%20on%20May%2019%2C%20a%20week%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20handed%20over%20the%20control%20of%20services%20in%20Delhi%20excluding%20police%2C%20public%20order%20and%20land%20to%20the%20elected%20government%2C%20headed%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20of%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20AAP%20leader%20Raghav%20Chadha%20said%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20that%20bill%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20fraud%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bconstitutional%20sin%26quot%3B%20aimed%20at%20taking%20away%20the%20powers%20of%20an%20elected%20government%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20non-NDA%20parties%20to%20support%20AAP%20in%20the%20House%20against%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691426280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F8gl8qu88_amit-shah-ndtv_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-services-bill-in-no-way-violates-supreme-court-judgment-amit-shah-4277505%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20services%20bill%20in%20no%20way%20violates%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-services-bill-in-no-way-violates-supreme-court-judgment-amit-shah-4277505%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-services-bill-in-no-way-violates-supreme-court-judgment-amit-shah-4277505%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-services-bill-in-no-way-violates-supreme-court-judgment-amit-shah-4277505%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ten%20Reasons%20Why%20The%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Law%20Doesn't%20Empower%20Citizens%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06095248%2FUntitled-design-4.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%202023%20has%20been%20passed%20today%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20After%20years%20of%20exhaustive%20public%20consultations%20and%20multiple%20drafts%2C%20this%20seemingly%20final%20version%20of%20the%20Bill%20is%20being%20termed%20the%20simplest%20of%20all%20drafts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20many%20concerns%20around%20how%20the%20Bill%20continues%20to%20ignore%20purpose%20limitation%20and%20push%20for%20further%20data%20collection%20through%20duties%20on%20data%20principals.%20But%20will%20this%20Bill%20really%20empower%20us%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Data%20empowerment%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20the%20magic%20term%20that%20has%20been%20used%20to%20push%20various%20centralised%20databases%20onto%20the%20citizens%20of%20India.%20We%20were%20told%20we%20can%20become%20rich%20by%20exchanging%20our%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20so%20far%2C%20the%20problems%20in%20Digital%20India%E2%80%99s%20software%20designs%20have%20resulted%20in%20people%20being%20exploited%20and%20harmed%20by%20loan%20apps%20and%20social%20engineering%20fraud.%20Neither%20of%20these%20will%20stop%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20as%20long%20as%20the%20data%20proliferation%20continues%2C%20and%20this%20Bill%20won%E2%80%99t%20stop%20that%20either.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20is%20a%20long%20list%20of%20issues%20the%20Bill%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20address%20and%20which%20will%20be%20litigated%20further%20in%20the%20courts%2C%20with%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20privacy%20recognised%20as%20part%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F127517806%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPuttaswamy%20vs%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20should%20help%20us%20understand%20who%20the%20Bill%20is%20empowering.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20The%20practice%20of%20mandating%20people%20to%20link%20their%20Aadhaar%20will%20continue%20and%20expand%20to%20create%20360-degree%20profile%20databases%2C%20as%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20expected%20to%20pass%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fregistration-of-births-deaths-aadhaar-voter-id%5C%22%3ERegistration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Indians%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20part%20with%20their%20personal%20information%20from%20birth%20to%20death.%20The%20Bill%20ignores%20purpose%20limitation%20entirely%20and%20says%20that%20any%20data%20collected%20can%20be%20used%20for%20other%20purposes%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E2.%20All%20personal%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20government%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20surveillance%20institutions%2C%20with%20no%20mention%20of%20restrictions%20on%20surveillance%20in%20the%20Bill.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhome-ministry-allows-10-central-agencies-to-engage-in-electronic-interception%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eten%20agencies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20authorised%20under%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20and%20various%20policing%20departments%20will%20continue%20to%20collect%20personal%20data%20without%20any%20restrictions.%20A%20blanket%20exception%20has%20been%20made%20for%20the%20police%20to%20use%20360-degree%20profile%20databases%20like%20NATGRID%20for%20surveillance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E3.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20Income%20Tax%20authorities%E2%80%99%20raids%20on%20the%20Opposition%20and%20tax%20surveillance%20of%20every%20resident%20in%20India%20will%20go%20unchecked.%20A%20weapon%20in%20the%20arsenal%20of%20the%20government%20to%20suppress%20any%20form%20of%20dissent%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20that%20stops%20these%20institutions%20to%20raid%20even%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fit-department-surveys-raghav-bahls-home-quint-and-the-news-minute-offices%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emedia%20houses%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20to%20clone%20their%20mobile%20phones%20and%20laptops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E4.%20Facial%20recognition%20and%20other%20biometric%20technologies%20will%20continue%20to%20flourish%2C%20for%20tasks%20ranging%20from%20basic%20attendance%20usage%20to%20surveillance.%20The%20government%20could%20grant%20exemptions%20to%20companies%20involved%20in%20facial%20recognition%20to%20collect%20this%20data%20in%20order%20to%20build%20surveillance%20systems.%20Projects%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdigi-yatra-privacy-biometric-travel%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDigi%20Yatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20facial%20recognition%20for%20de-duplication%20for%20KYC%2C%20access%20management%2C%20monitoring%20of%20work%2C%20and%20surveillance%20will%20thrive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E5.%20This%20Bill%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20the%20government%20from%20forcing%20you%20to%20submit%20your%20health%20data%20and%20use%20it%20as%20they%20want%20during%20and%20after%20health%20emergencies.%20From%20Aarogya%20Setu%20to%20Co-WIN%2C%20there%20are%20blanket%20exemptions%20on%20how%20much%20personal%20data%20can%20be%20collected%20and%20how%20they%20use%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fcowin-data-leak-is-a-sign-india-needs-to-rethink-its-digital-public-infrastructure-strategy%5C%22%3ECoWIN%20Data%20Leak%20Is%20a%20Sign%20India%20Needs%20to%20Rethink%20its%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%20Strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20provision%20in%20the%20Bill%20to%20demand%20deletions%20of%20personal%20data.%20Even%20after%20the%20COVID-19%20vaccination%20drive%20is%20over%2C%20we%20are%20still%20not%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fcowin-data-breach-citizens-must-be-allowed-to-delete-personal-data-from-govt-databases%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eallowed%20to%20delete%20Co-WIN%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20any%20other%20health%20data%20the%20government%20collected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E6.%20All%20employers%20are%20exempt%20to%20collect%20the%20personal%20data%20of%20their%20employees%20as%20they%20see%20fit.%20Every%20company%20from%20Uber%2C%20Ola%20and%20Swiggy%20to%20Urban%20Company%20can%20continue%20to%20collect%20the%20personal%20information%20of%20their%20employees%20%E2%80%93%20including%20facial%20biometrics%20%E2%80%93%20and%20even%20use%20it%20to%20fire%20them%20or%20stop%20them%20from%20working%20for%20their%20platforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20surveillance%20of%20employees%E2%80%99%20devices%20%E2%80%93%20from%20phones%20to%20work%20machines%20%E2%80%93%20will%20continue%20to%20go%20unchecked.%20Government%20employees%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20share%20their%20facial%20biometrics%20for%20attendance%2C%20and%20surveillance%20of%20their%20work%20through%20cameras.%20With%20the%20push%20for%20real-time%20work%2C%20anganwadi%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fhow-digital-snooping-on-sanitation-workers-is-worsening-their-struggles%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esanitation%20workers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20will%20continuously%20be%20monitored%20by%20various%20apps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E7.%20Google%2C%20Facebook%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Apple%20and%20other%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20can%20continue%20to%20use%20your%20personal%20information%20that%20you%20publicly%20share.%20This%20Bill%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20any%20personal%20data%20collection%20by%20these%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20and%20is%20unlikely%20to%20result%20in%20any%20major%20changes%20in%20how%20the%20entire%20IT%20industry%20operates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20duties%20in%20the%20Bill%20force%20us%20to%20not%20to%20supply%20any%20false%20information%20to%20these%20or%20any%20other%20companies%2C%20killing%20anonymity.%20The%20government%20can%20demand%20all%20of%20this%20data%20from%20these%20companies%20with%20no%20oversight.%20This%20Bill%20at%20best%20forces%20these%20companies%20to%20allow%20you%20to%20delete%20your%20personal%20data%2C%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20exit%20these%20platforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E8.%20The%20Bill%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fregressive-amendments-to-rti-act-ncpri-flags-concerns-over-digital-personal-data-protection-bill%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eweakens%20the%20RTI%20Act%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20us%20to%20access%20any%20personal%20information%2C%20including%20the%20names%20of%20the%20bureaucrats%20that%20are%20signing%20key%20government%20files.%20This%20will%20create%20an%20information%20asymmetry%20between%20the%20state%20and%20citizenry%2C%20where%20the%20state%20knows%20everything%20about%20the%20citizenry%20but%20citizens%20know%20nothing%20about%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchanges-to-rti-act-rs-500-crore-fine-five-pitfalls-to-watch-out-for-in-the-data-protection-law%5C%22%3EChanges%20to%20RTI%20Act%2C%20Rs%20500%20Crore%20Fine%3A%20Five%20Pitfalls%20to%20Watch%20Out%20for%20in%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Law%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20A%20key%20feature%20of%20Digital%20India%20and%20surveillance%20capitalism%20is%20the%20use%20of%20personal%20data%20for%20financial%20services%2C%20from%20loan%20apps%20to%20insurance.%20The%20Bill%20provides%20these%20companies%20exemptions%20to%20process%20the%20personal%20data%20of%20any%20loan%20defaulter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20means%20that%20private%20companies%20are%20allowed%20to%20collect%20personal%20data%20from%20anyone%20who%20takes%20loans.%20That%20data%20will%20be%20deleted%20once%20the%20loan%20is%20paid%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20processed%20in%20any%20way%20the%20company%20wants%20until%20it%20recovers%20the%20loan%20amount.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20loan%20defaulter%20databases%20that%20will%20be%20used%20for%20the%20further%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fas-ai-based-loan-apps-boom-in-india-some-borrowers-miss-out%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eeconomic%20exclusion%20of%20marginalised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20people%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E10.%20The%20Data%20Protection%20Board%20that%20the%20Bill%20sanctions%20will%20be%20set%20up%20by%20the%20government%2C%20making%20it%20less%20independent%2C%20and%20prone%20to%20acting%20at%20the%20whims%20of%20the%20powerful%20bureaucrats%2C%20businessmen%20and%20politicians%20of%20India.%20Even%20if%20there%20is%20a%20data%20breach%2C%20the%20data%20protection%20board%20will%20act%20partially%2C%20with%20no%20clear%20independence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20a%20privacy%20Bill%2C%20but%20a%20mere%20data%20processing%20Bill%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20address%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20common%20citizen.%20This%20Bill%20is%20just%20a%20rubber%20stamp%20at%20the%20end%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20digitisation%20process%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20empower%20any%20citizens%2C%20but%20only%20businesses%20and%20government%20institutions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20travesty%20that%20a%20powerful%20judgement%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPuttaswamy%20vs%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20this%20unjust%20form%20which%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20contested%20in%20the%20courts.%20There%20may%20not%20be%20any%20relief%20from%20these%20mandatory%20data%20collections%20by%20Digital%20India%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Law%20Empower%20the%20Public%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691426032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06095248%2FUntitled-design-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwill-the-data-protection-law-empower-the-public%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20the%20ten-point%20list%20of%20issues%20this%20Bill%20doesn't%20address%20is%20unchecked%20data%20collection%20by%20employees%2C%20the%20weakening%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20sanctioning%20of%20a%20data%20protection%20board%20that%20will%20be%20beholden%20to%20those%20in%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwill-the-data-protection-law-empower-the-public%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bipasha%20Karan's%20cutest%20pictures%20with%20Devi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691425800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102510097%2Cimgsize-51978.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fbipasha-basu-and-karan-singh-grovers-cutest-pictures-with-daughter-devi%2Fphotostory%2F102510097.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102510097.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%8BBipasha%20Basu%20and%20Karan%20Singh%20Grover's%20cutest%20pictures%20with%20daughter%20Devi%20%E2%80%8B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fbipasha-basu-and-karan-singh-grovers-cutest-pictures-with-daughter-devi%2Fphotostory%2F102510097.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Mistakes%20Have%20Happened%20But..%5C%22%3A%20Ex-India%20Star%20On%20Coach%20Dravid's%20Tenure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Kaif%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F247-mohammad-kaif-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Kaif%3C%2Fa%3E%20asserted%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20this%20year%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20judged%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20two%20T20I%20losses%20in%20the%20West%20Indies.%20India%2C%20after%20winning%20the%20two-Test%20series%20and%20ODIs%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20are%20trailing%200-2%20in%20the%20five-match%20T20I%20series%2C%20leading%20to%20criticism%20over%20the%20side's%20preparations%20ahead%20of%20two%20major%20competitions%20--%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kaif%20said%20at%20a%20function%20here%20that%20the%20fears%20of%20India%20under-performing%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20were%20unfounded%2C%20although%20he%20indicated%20that%20pace%20bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20have%20to%20be%20fully%20fit%20for%20the%20hosts%20to%20end%20the%20title%20drought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20lost%20just%20two%20matches%20(T20Is%20against%20West%20Indies)%2C%20so%20we%20do%20not%20need%20to%20get%20overly%20concerned.%20I%20am%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20negative%20reaction%20after%20the%20two%20losses.%20But%20I%20will%20only%20say%20that%20our%20team%20is%20extremely%20competitive.%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20judge%20(India)%20on%20two%20back-to-back%20losses%20(in%20the%20West%20Indies).%20The%20only%20thing%20is%20that%20key%20players%20are%20missing%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaif%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBumrah%20missing%20is%20the%20biggest%20factor.%20If%20he%20recovers%20fully...%20one%20aspect%20is%20to%20complete%20the%20recovery%20and%20the%20other%20aspect%20is%20to%20gain%20match%20fitness.%20If%20he%20regains%20that%20(match%20fitness)%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20gain%20for%20Team%20India.%20If%20Bumrah%20is%20fully%20fit%2C%20we%20have%20a%20great%20chance%20of%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kaif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20will%20be%20staging%20a%20comeback%20during%20the%20T20%20series%20against%20Ireland%20after%20being%20out%20of%20action%20for%20almost%20a%20year%20following%20a%20back%20surgery%2C%20and%20Kaif%20attributed%20the%2029-year-old%20quick's%20absence%20for%20India's%20string%20of%20losses%20in%20major%20competitions%20during%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20discussing%20that%20the%20(India)%20team%20under%20(chief%20coach)%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20lost%20the%20(T20)%20Asia%20Cup%20(last%20year)%2C%20the%20(T20)%20World%20Cup%20in%20Australi