bly%20to%20discuss%20the%20ongoing%20turmoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20now%20reached%20the%20door%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthouba%20Khuraijam%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20and%20some%20other%20representatives%20of%20the%20Committee%20went%20to%20the%20PMO%20to%20physically%20submit%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-cocomi-demands-special-manipur-legislative-assembly-session-before-august-5-623592-2023-07-29%5C%22%3Eresolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20taken%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20on%20July%2029%20in%20Imphal%20calling%20for%20such%20a%20session.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20asked%20to%20spell%20out%20why%20such%20a%20session%20is%20particularly%20needed%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20Athouba%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20demand%20has%20been%20raised%20from%20our%20side%20because%20we%20have%20not%20seen%20any%20initiative%20from%20the%20legislators%20or%20the%20state%20government%20to%20discuss%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House.%20The%20assembly%20is%20not%20dissolved%2C%20so%20it%20must%20assemble%20to%20deliberate%20on%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20discussing%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20from%20a%20set%20of%20MLAs.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%2010%20MLAs%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%20have%20stated%20their%20individual%20positions%20on%20the%20matter%20which%20should%20be%20stated%20also%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House.%20There%20are%20outside%20forces%20acting%20in%20the%20state%3B%20people%20are%20asking%2C%20where%20is%20the%20assembly%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20noticed%20some%20sitting%20MLAs%20engaging%20in%20things%20which%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%2C%20being%20a%20member%20of%20the%20assembly.%20Such%20things%20must%20be%20put%20on%20record.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20July%2029%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-cocomi-demands-special-manipur-legislative-assembly-session-before-august-5-623592-2023-07-29%5C%22%3Eresolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20taken%20as%20part%20of%20a%20mass%20rally%20held%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley.%20As%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20around%20two%20lakh%20people%20took%20part%20in%20that%20rally%20where%20some%20speakers%20also%20criticized%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20to%20quell%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20border%20state.%20In%20that%20session%2C%20those%20assembled%20urged%20the%20Governor%2C%20the%20speaker%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20hold%20that%20special%20session%20by%20August%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20it%2C%20several%20other%20valley-based%20civil%20society%20organisations%20had%20also%20taken%20a%20similar%20resolution.%20On%20July%2027%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20information%20and%20public%20relations%20minister%20Sapam%20Ranjan%20told%20the%20local%20press%20that%20the%20Cabinet%20had%20approved%20a%20special%20session%20and%20the%20request%20had%20been%20forwarded%20to%20the%20governor.%20Ranjan%20said%20the%20Cabinet%20has%20asked%20for%20a%20special%20session%20in%20the%20third%20week%20of%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20hold%20the%20session%20by%20the%20August%205%20deadline%20of%20the%20COCOMI%2C%20it%20has%20now%20called%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20boycott%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20reaching%20out%20to%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%20demanding%20a%20separate%20administration%20for%20the%20Kuki%20residents%20of%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20if%20he%20would%20attend%20such%20a%20session%20if%20the%20governor%20accepts%20the%20Cabinet%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20categorically%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20would%20give%20assurance%20of%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Kuki%20MLAs%20going%20to%20Imphal%20to%20attend%20the%20assembly%20session%3F%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I%20would%20say%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20and%20also%20not%20necessary%20to%20participate%20in%20it%20as%20the%20separation%20of%20the%20state%20is%20complete.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07195859%2Fmanipur_assembly_session_2_20150625_1176793276.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07195859%2Fmanipur_assembly_session_2_20150625_1176793276.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07195859%2Fmanipur_assembly_session_2_20150625_1176793276-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667037%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20Assembly.%20Photo%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.assembly.mn.gov.in%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20asked%20whether%20he%20is%20still%20hopeful%20of%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20relenting%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20to%20the%20Kukis%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20hope%2C%20we%20hope%2C%20it%20would.%20Also%2C%20BJP%20is%20a%20national%20party%3B%20it%20is%20not%20about%20fulfilling%20the%20political%20ambitions%20of%20someone%20by%20causing%20communal%20violence.%20I%20hope%20it%20takes%20action%20against%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C