urces%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20volumes%20of%20inscriptions%2C%20literary%20texts%2C%20and%20archival%20documents%2C%20as%20well%20as%20important%20secondary%20sources%20of%20a%20high%20academic%20standing%20were%20housed%20in%20the%20library%20%E2%80%A6%20The%20library%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20of%20immense%20value%20for%20students%20at%20the%20post-graduate%20and%20research%20levels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20following%20the%20CHS%20example%2C%20other%20centres%20have%20also%20set%20up%20departmental%20libraries%20in%20the%20university.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20wrote%20about%20how%20the%20CHS%20received%20grants%20from%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20specifically%20to%20build%20the%20library%20and%20later%20to%20double%20its%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20this%20history%20of%20the%20CHS%20library%2C%20as%20faculty%20who%20have%20nurtured%20this%20institution%20over%20past%20several%20decades%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20the%20library%E2%80%99s%20relocation%20and%20dispersal%20would%20essentially%20destroy%20this%20fine%20institution%20which%20was%20funded%20specifically%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20letter%20concluded%20by%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20historians%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20JNU%20administration%20seems%20to%20have%20decided%20to%20move%20the%20CHS%20library%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20even%20consulting%20the%20CHS%20faculty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20full%20copy%20of%20their%20letter%20has%20been%20reproduced%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJNU%20students%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20library%E2%80%99s%20future%20last%20week%20when%20speculation%20arose%20that%20the%20administration%20was%20going%20to%20shut%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMaktoob%20Media%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaktoobmedia.com%2Flatest-news%2Fjnu-to-shut-down-centre-for-historical-studies-library-students-say-no