ts%20pertaining%20to%20the%20relocation%20of%20the%20CHS%20CAS%20Library%20and%20reallocation%20of%20the%20Library%20Building%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadam%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20the%20former%20faculty%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Historical%20Studies%2C%20are%20shocked%20to%20hear%20that%20the%20CHS%20library%20building%20is%20being%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20administration%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20the%20need%20for%20space%20for%20new%20centres%20that%20are%20being%20established%20within%20the%20university.%20Since%20the%20grant%20for%20the%20building%20of%20the%20CHS%20library%20was%20received%20expressly%20for%20this%20purpose%20from%20the%20UGC%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20disturbing%20to%20hear%20that%20the%20building%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20put%20to%20alternate%20use%20after%20several%20decades%20of%20its%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CHS%20received%20a%20Department%20of%20Special%20Assistance%20(DSA)%20status%20from%20the%20UGC%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20that%20was%20aimed%20at%20developing%20the%20research%20and%20teaching%20in%20the%20Centre.%20The%20faculty%20requested%20that%20the%20grant%20promised%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20used%20not%20for%20more%20faculty%20positions%2C%20as%20was%20the%20current%20practice%2C%20but%20to%20build%20an%20exclusive%20departmental%20library%20of%20the%20CHS%2C%20necessary%20for%20teaching%20and%20research%20at%20an%20advanced%20level.%20Permission%20was%20given%20and%20the%20grant%20received%20was%20used%20to%20construct%20the%20CHS%20library%20building.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20the%20CHS%20faculty%20in%20fact%20gave%20up%20its%20own%20promotion%20avenues%20by%20choosing%20to%20build%20the%20library%20rather%20then%20receive%20more%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsix-tables-that-tell-the-story-of-academic-unfreedom-in-india%5C%22%3ESix%20Tables%20that%20Tell%20the%20Story%20of%20Academic%20Unfreedom%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CHS%20faculty%20brought%20resources%20from%20archives%20and%20libraries%20across%20India%20and%20the%20world%20(from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20French%20Archives)%20to%20the%20library%20to%20facilitate%20teaching%20and%20%C2%A0research.%20A%20rich%20collection%20of%20primary%20sources%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20volumes%20of%20inscriptions%2C%20literary%20texts%2C%20and%20archival%20documents%2C%20as%20well%20as%20important%20secondary%20sources%20of%20a%20high%20academic%20standing%20were%20housed%20in%20the%20library.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0The%20library%20was%20able%20to%20bid%20for%20and%20get%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%20the%20rich%20personal%20collection%20of%20the%20eminent%20scholar%20Bernard%20Cohn.%20Collections%20of%20other%20eminent%20scholars%20like%20Satish%20Chandra%20and%20D.N.%20Gupta%20were%20also%20housed%20in%20this%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CHS%20library%20now%20houses%20a%20repository%20that%20was%20carefully%20built%20by%20the%20faculty%20over%20decades%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20research%20and%20teaching%20needs%20of%20the%20Centre.%20The%20library%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20of%20immense%20value%20for%20students%20at%20the%20post-graduate%20and%20research%20levels.%20An%20intensive%20tutorial%20based%20and%20research%20based%20teaching%20programme%20that%20the%20CHS%20conducts%20would%20have%20been%20virtually%20impossible%20without%20such%20a%20departmental%20library%20available%20to%20the%20students.%C2%A0%20In%20fact%2C%20following%20the%20CHS%20example%20other%20centres%20have%20also%20set%20up%20departmental%20libraries%20in%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20library%20resources%20and%20heavy%20demand%20for%20its%20usage%20that%20the%20need%20was%20felt%20to%20expand%20the%20library.%20After%20the%20CHS%20was%20deemed%20a%20Centre%20for%20Advanced%20Study%20by%20the%20UGC%20another%20grant%20was%20sought%20and%20received%20which%20enabled%20a%20near%20doubling%20of%20the%20space%20in%20the%20CHS%20library%20by%20adding%20a%20floor%20and%20extending%20the%20existing%20CHS%20library%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20history%20of%20the%20CHS%20library%2C%20as%20faculty%20who%20have%20nurtured%20this%20institution%20over%20past%20several%20decades%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20the%20library%E2%80%99s%20relocation%20and%20dispersal%20would%20essentially%20destroy%20this%20fine%20institution%20which%20was%20funded%20specifically%20for%20the%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20therefore%20sincerely%20urge%20the%20University%20to%20reverse%20this%20hasty%20decision%20which%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20taken%20without%20even%20consulting%20the%20CHS%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfs.%20Romila%20Thapar%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnHarbans%20Mukhia%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnJ.N.%20Panikkar%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnSuvira%20Jaiswal%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnMridula%20Mukherjee%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnDilbagh%20Singh%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnAditya%20Mukherjee%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnNeeladri%20Bhattacharya%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnYogesh%20Sharma%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnArvind%20Sinha%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnKumkum%20Roy%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnRanabir%20Chakrabarty%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnSucheta%20Mahajan%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnJanaki%20Nair%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnRadhika%20Singha%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnSupriya%20Verma%3Cbr%3E%5CnTanika%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691413210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07173559%2FCentre-for-Historical-Studies.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fformer-faculty-say-jnu-chs-library-reolcation-will-destroy-centre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20the%20JNU%20administration%20has%20clarified%20that%20it%20is%20not%20shutting%20down%20the%20Centre%20for%20Historical%20Studies'%20library%2C%20concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20about%20whether%20its%20new%20location%20can%20fully%20accommodate%20its%20extensive%20contents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22can