of%20the%20affidavit%20presented%20to%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20and%20Thounaojam%20has%20named%20all%20the%20people%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20said%2C%20Tamal%20Saha%20of%20News%20The%20Truth%20revealed%20this%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20I%20have%20done%20a%20subsequent%20interview%20with%20Thounaojam%20%E2%80%93%20where%20she%20goes%20into%20the%20matter%20in%20greater%20detail%20and%20with%20greater%20analysis%20%E2%80%93%20because%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20proper%20that%20this%20should%20be%20fully%20known%20to%20the%20people%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20Thounaojam%20faces%20several%20defamation%20cases%20brought%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20you%20must%20judge%20this%20story%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FK0rZN3dQ51w%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691411408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07171749%2Fca8baaae-e941-4913-9798-f662f0289fb2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fformer-manipur-asp-thounaojam-brinda-details-how-biren-singh-pressured-her-to-drop-2018-drug-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20June%202018%2C%20Thounaojam%20had%20raided%20the%20office%20of%20former%20ADC%20chairman%20of%20Chandel%20Lukhosei%20Zou%2C%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20found%20drugs%20worth%20crores%20in%20the%20raid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fformer-manipur-asp-thounaojam-brinda-details-how-biren-singh-pressured-her-to-drop-2018-drug-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%