%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%8F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhAvAHSxUBr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FhAvAHSxUBr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20(%40nishikant_dubey)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnishikant_dubey%2Fstatus%2F1688445325814747138%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20ED%20conducted%20raids%20on%20the%20residences%20of%20several%20officials%20and%20journalists%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fenforcement-directorate-newsclick-raids%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20owner%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20editor%20Pranjal%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20were%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20a%20probe%20related%20to%20foreign%20remittances%20and%20charges%20of%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubey%20said%20that%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20part%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%20gang%2C%20%3Cem%3ETukde%20Tukde%3C%2Fem%3E%20gang%E2%80%9D%20that%20wants%20to%20break%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20its%20owner%20are%20helping%20these%20forces%2C%20and%20%5Bthat%5D%20the%20money%20has%20been%20given%20to%20Naxalites%20and%20to%20journalists%20like%20Rohini%20Singh%20and%20Swati%20Chaturvedi%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20an%20atmosphere%20against%20India%E2%80%9D%20for%20which%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20have%20been%20given%20Chinese%20money%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Congress%20received%20money%20from%20China%20between%202005%20and%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetween%202005%20and%202014%2C%20whenever%20there%20was%20a%20crisis%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20received%20money%20from%20China.%20In%202008%2C%20they%20invited%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20In%202017%2C%20they%20were%20talking%20to%20the%20Chinese%20during%20the%20Doklam%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20took%20the%20names%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20and%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20and%20said%20they%20are%20associated%20with%20the%20Chinese.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(Congress)%20want%20to%20break%20India%20by%20using%20Chinese%20social%20media%20and%20journalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20links%20with%20the%20Chinese%20need%20to%20be%20probed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20about%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fneville-roy-singham-china-propaganda.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20article%20claims%20that%20an%20American%20millionaire%2C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%2C%20works%20closely%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government%20media%20machine%20to%20finance%20its%20propaganda%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20a%20think%20tank%20in%20Massachusetts%20to%20an%20event%20space%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20from%20a%20political%20party%20in%20South%20Africa%20to%20news%20organisations%20in%20India%20and%20Brazil%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20tracked%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20groups%20linked%20to%20Mr.%20Singham%20that%20mix%20progressive%20advocacy%20with%20Chinese%20government%20talking%20points%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20article%20said%20that%20corporate%20filings%20show%20that%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20network%20%E2%80%9Cfinanced%20a%20news%20site%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20sprinkled%20its%20coverage%20with%20Chinese%20government%20talking%20points.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20refers%20to%20a%20video%20titled%20%E2%80%9CChina%E2%80%99s%20history%20continues%20to%20inspire%20the%20working%20classes%E2%80%9D%20on%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPurkayastha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fstatement-newsclick-regarding-allegations%2527%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20evening%2C%20denying%20allegations%20that%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20a%20mouthpiece%20for%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20past%2012%20hours%2C%20various%20false%20and%20misleading%20allegations%20have%20been%20levelled%20against%20Newsclick%20which%20pertain%20to%20matters%20that%20are%20currently%20%3Cem%3Esub%20judice%3C%2Fem%3E%20before%20courts%20in%20India.%20We%20respect%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20legal%20process%20and%20do%20not%20intend%20to%20indulge%20in%20a%20media%20trial%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20statement%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continues%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20independent%20news%20organisation%2C%20and%20any%20insinuation%20that%20we%20function%20as%20a%20mouth-piece%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20or%20other%20interests%20is%20false.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20reiterate%20our%20faith%20in%20the%20Indian%20Courts%2C%20and%20are%20confident%20that%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20function%20in%20accordance%20with%20Indian%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPurkayastha%20also%20referred%20to%20a%20decision%20by%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20granting%20interim%20protection%20from%20arrest%20to%20various%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20employees%2C%20and%20recalled%20a%20Delhi%20magistrate%E2%80%99s%20dismissal%20of%20a%20complaint%20by%20income%20tax%20authorities%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20account%20of%20lack%20of%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENames%20expunged%20from%20records%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaturvedi%20and%20Singh%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20instead%20of%20making%20claims%20inside%20parliament%20using%20his%20parliamentary%20privileges%2C%20Dubey%20should%20try%20making%20these%20claims%20outside%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20parliamentarian%2C%20he%20should%20not%20be%20lying%20in%20parliament%20by%20using%20names%20who%20have%20never%20worked%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20reason%20he%20is%20doing%20this%20is%20because%20we%20have%20always%20countered%20him.%20I%20would%20urge%20him%20to%20repeat%20what%20he%20said%20inside%20the%20House%20outside%20parliament%20because%20there%20can%20be%20legal%20repercussions%20to%20whatever%20you%20say%20and%20there%20is%20no%20parliamentary%20privilege%20outside%20the%20House%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaturvedi%20shared%20a%20record%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20proceedings%20and%20that%20her%20name%20had%20been%20expunged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20record%20also%20showed%20that%20along%20with%20her%2C%20Singh%2C%20Purkayastha%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20names%20had%20also%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDubey%20has%20used%20his%20parliamentary%20privilege%20and%20he%20has%20taken%20my%20name%20in%20the%20House%20but%20I%20challenge%20anyone%20to%20show%20if%20I%20have%20ever%20taken%20even%20a%20penny%20from%3Cem%3E%20NewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20have%20never%20contributed%20to%20them%2C%20never%20written%20for%20them%20and%20never%20even%20appeared%20on%20any%20of%20their%20videos%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chaturvedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20BJP%20MP%20misusing%20my%20name.%20While%20my%20name%20has%20been%20expunged%2C%20this%20government%20has%20done%20everything%20it%20can%20to%20intimidate%20me%20and%20to%20silence%20me.%20This%20is%20another%20attempt%20to%20silence%20me%20but%20I%20will%20not%20be%20silenced%20and%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20my%20work%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20comments%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20adjourned%20till%202%20pm%20as%20opposition%20MPs%20protested%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20in%20the%20House%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAnand_Journ%2Fstatus%2F1688462947800981504%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Ewrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Speaker%3C%2Fa%3E%20Om%20Birla%20and%20said%20that%20Dubey%20started%20levelling%20%E2%80%9Clibellous%20and%20defamatory%20charges%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20House%2C%20without%20having%20given%20any%20notice%2C%20let%20alone%20take%20the%20permission%20of%20the%20chair.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20demanded%20that%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20statement%20against%20Gandhi%20be%20expunged%20from%20the%20record%20and%20an%20inquiry%20be%20conducted%20into%20how%20such%20an%20allegation%20was%20permitted%20to%20be%20raised%20on%20the%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20later%20on%20Monday%2C%20Union%20ministers%20Anurag%20Thakur%20and%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20repeated%20their%20claims%20against%20the%20Congress%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCongress%2C%20China%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20part%20of%20an%20umbilical%20cord.%20In%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Nakli%20Mohabbat%20Ki%20Dukaan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20Chinese%20goods%20can%20be%20seen%20clearly.%20His%20love%20for%20China%20can%20be%20seen.%20They%20have%20an%20anti-India%20agenda%2C%20and%20%5Bthey%5D%20ran%20a%20break%20India%20campaign%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1688462143904153602%5C%22%3Esaid%20Thakur.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrasekhar%20said%20that%20the%20narratives%20put%20forward%20by%20platforms%20like%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20echoed%20by%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20narratives%20that%20are%20put%20out%20by%20platforms%20like%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20other%20platforms%20that%20are%20operating%20in%20concert%20are%20echoed%20almost%20blandly%20in%20a%20similar%20fashion%20by%20this%20political%20leader%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20goes%20abroad%20and%20says%20exactly%20the%20same%20things%20%E2%80%93%20democracy%20is%20under%20danger%2C%20judiciary%20is%20compromised%2C%20EVMs%20are%20compromised.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20complex%20conspiracy.%20This%20is%20a%20network%20of%20operators%20being%20funded%2C%20being%20fanned%20by%20vested%20interests%20outside%20the%20country%2C%20who%20are%20opposed%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20rise%2C%20opposed%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20presence%20in%20the%20global%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1688467961869451265%5C%22%3Ehe%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20refuted%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20and%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CPM%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20are%20experts%20in%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%93%20lying.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20posed%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1688488006309543936%5C%22%3E%20ten%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20dared%20the%20government%20to%20answer%20them%2C%20including%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20Chinese%20encroachment%2C%20and%20when%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20April%202020%20will%20be%20restored%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20as%20well%20as%20questions%20on%20how%20far%20China%20entered%20the%20official%20territory%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691409869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F171825