66427441.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20'Data%20Protection'%20Undermines%20People%E2%80%99s%20Protection%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07151000%2Fprateek-jaiswal-4Hp4ceaIIwE-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20much%20that%20can%20be%20and%20has%20been%20said%20about%20the%20data%20protection%20Bill%2C%20which%20was%20just%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20a%20voice%20vote.%20Like%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Bill%20removes%20rather%20than%20establishes%20boundaries%20around%20what%20the%20government%20can%20do%20with%20people%E2%80%99s%20personal%20data%20by%2C%20for%20example%2C%20proposing%20a%20Data%20Protection%20Board%20lacking%20independence%2C%20or%20by%20being%20silent%20on%20surveillance.%20Or%20how%2C%20in%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20the%20state%20going%20after%20those%20seeking%20justice%2C%20the%20proposed%20law%20also%20allows%20for%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Board%20to%20penalise%20%E2%80%9Cfrivolous%E2%80%9D%20grievances%20or%20complaints%2C%20thereby%20going%20after%20the%20very%20people%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20protect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20article%20is%20not%20about%20any%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20protection%20is%20not%20an%20end%20in%20itself.%20It%20is%20the%20means%20to%20protect%20the%20people%20to%20whom%20the%20data%20pertains.%20If%20a%20data%20protection%20law%20protects%20only%20the%20person%E2%80%99s%20data%20but%20not%20the%20person%2C%20then%20it%20is%20not%20serving%20its%20purpose.%20Globally%2C%20most%20data%20protection%20legislation%20is%20rightly%20built%20on%20the%20principle%20of%20consent.%20But%20the%20way%20that%20consent%20is%20usually%20operationalised%20in%20law%20gives%20people%20very%20little%20control%20to%20protect%20their%20data%2C%20including%20the%20approach%20that%20has%20been%20adopted%20in%20the%20present%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20digital%20consent%20frameworks%20merely%20allow%20for%20a%20yes%20or%20no%20answer.%20More%20sophisticated%20consent%20managers%20allow%20for%20more%20granular%20sharing%20of%20data%2C%20allowing%20people%20to%20respond%20to%20which%20data%20they%20want%20to%20share%20and%20select%20which%20purposes%20they%20want%20to%20provide%20consent%20for.%20A%20wider%20framework%20which%20creates%20space%20for%20discussion%20and%20allows%20people%20to%20suggest%20rather%20than%20respond%20to%20what%20digital%20services%20can%20do%20with%20their%20data%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20properly%20conceived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20the%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20Won't%20Stop%20Data%20Proliferation%20in%20Digital%20India%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fdata-protection-bull-proliferation-digital-india%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Stop%20Data%20Proliferation%20in%20Digital%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20have%20little%20meaningful%20choice%20to%20not%20use%20WhatsApp%20to%20be%20in%20touch%20with%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20as%20well%20as%20for%20work.%20Refusing%20consent%20to%20WhatsApp%E2%80%99s%20terms%20of%20service%20practically%20means%20staying%20less%20in%20touch%20with%20those%20I%20love%20and%20work%20with%20%E2%80%93%20not%20a%20choice%20most%20people%20will%20make.%20Similarly%2C%20taxi%20drivers%20and%20other%20gig%20workers%20can%E2%80%99t%20really%20opt%20out%20of%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20ride-sharing%20and%20delivery%20apps%20and%20say%20no%20to%20them%2C%20since%20they%20have%20EMIs%20to%20pay%20and%20are%20financially%20locked%20in.%20Likewise%2C%20current%20shopping%20habits%20make%20it%20increasingly%20hard%20for%20retail%20businesspersons%20to%20not%20be%20on%20popular%20e-commerce%20websites%2C%20often%20on%20conditions%20unfavourable%20to%20the%20sellers.%20Therefore%2C%20meaningful%20data%20protection%20frameworks%20should%20allow%20people%20to%20decide%20how%20digital%20services%20can%20operate%20rather%20than%20the%20other%20way%20round.%20This%20is%20because%20even%20while%20consent%20is%20obtained%20in%20theory%2C%20often%20the%20real%20world%20allows%20for%20little%20choice%20in%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20surveillance%20state%2C%20data%20needs%20protection%20from%20those%20with%20commercial%20interests%20who%20abuse%20it%20against%20the%20financial%20interests%20of%20people.%20Data%20protection%20has%20a%20privacy%20component%20for%20ensuring%20the%20political%20rights%20of%20people%20as%20well%20as%20a%20commercial%20component%20for%20ascertaining%20economic%20rights.%20By%20looking%20at%20only%20privacy%20without%20safeguarding%20people%E2%80%99s%20financial%20interests%2C%20legislation%20will%20only%20be%20taking%20a%20half-hearted%20approach%20to%20data%20protection.%20For%20gig%20workers%2C%20those%20selling%20on%20online%20platforms%20and%20even%20people%20on%20the%20internet%20who%20receive%20spookily%20accurate%20targeted%20ads%2C%20current%20data%20protection%20regimes%20will%20merely%20assuage%20symptoms%20and%20not%20address%20the%20root%20cause%20%E2%80%93%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20have%20very%20little%20control%20on%20how%20their%20data%20is%20used%20beyond%20a%20yes%20or%20no%20consent.%20For%20genuine%20people%20protection%2C%20we%20must%20create%20laws%20that%20enable%20participatory%20governance%20of%20the%20digital%20services%20they%20use%20so%20that%20people%20can%20ensure%20that%20their%20data%20is%20protected%20from%20being%20used%20against%20their%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%20but%20gravely%2C%20this%20Bill%20is%20an%20example%20of%20how%20one%20right%20is%20used%20to%20compromise%20another%20right%20and%2C%20in%20the%20process%2C%20deny%20people%20both%20rights.%20While%20not%20adequately%20ensuring%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20privacy%2C%20this%20Bill%20is%20used%20as%20an%20occasion%20to%20also%20disastrously%20undermine%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act.%20This%20Bill%20seeks%20to%20break%20the%20harmony%20the%20RTI%20sought%20to%20create%20between%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20information%20and%20their%20right%20to%20privacy%2C%20by%20comprehensively%20amending%20the%20Section%208(1)j%20in%20the%20RTI%20Act%20that%20sought%20to%20create%20this%20balance%20by%20defining%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20RTI.%20The%20framers%20of%20this%20legislation%2C%20while%20dismantling%20this%20balance%2C%20have%20failed%20to%20provide%20an%20alternative%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20approach%20to%20data%20protection%20is%20not%20the%20be-all%20and%20end-all%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20protection%20online.%20People%E2%80%99s%20protection%20should%20be%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20end%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20a%20more%20well%20thought%20out%20approach%20to%20data%20protection%20legislation%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20means%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENachiket%20Udupa%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Mazdoor%20Kisan%20Shakti%20Sangathan%20(MKSS).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691401261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07151000%2Fprateek-jaiswal-4Hp4ceaIIwE-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhen-data-protection-undermines-peoples-protection%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Lok%20Sabha%20passed%20the%20contentious%20bill%20through%20a%20voice%20vote%20on%20Monday%20afternoon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhen-data-protection-undermines-peoples-protection%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20rice%20export%20ban%20now%20sparks%20concern%20that%20sugar%20might%20be%20next%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691400556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.busines