re.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-stays-rahul-gandhis-conviction-in-defamation-case-questions-lower-court-on-sentence%5C%22%3Ethe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20stayed%20his%20conviction%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20defamation%20case%20in%20which%20a%20Surat%20court%20had%20earlier%20found%20him%20guilty%20and%20handed%20him%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20two%20years%E2%80%99%20imprisonment%20%E2%80%93%20leading%20to%20his%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20had%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20conviction%2C%20after%20which%20Gandhi%20had%20appealed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restoration%20of%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20membership%20comes%20as%20Congress%20leaders%20as%20well%20as%20the%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20questioned%20the%20time%20taken%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20to%20restore%20his%20membership%2C%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20haste%20in%20which%20it%20had%20been%20revoked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20membership%20was%20revoked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-disqualified-lok-sabha-mp%5C%22%3Ewithin%2024%20hours%20of%20the%20Surat%20judgment.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20leader%20of%20house%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20had%20said%20over%20the%20weekend%20that%20he%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20the%20Secretariat%20but%20had%20not%20received%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSupreme%20Court%20said%20that%20it%20is%20staying%20the%20conviction%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20What%20does%20it%20mean%3F%20It%20means%20that%20he%20will%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Parliamentary%20proceedings%20once%20again%E2%80%A6The%20speed%20with%20which%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20disqualified%2C%20should%20be%20the%20same%20to%20reinstate%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1687742392374591488%5C%22%3Esaid%20Chowdhury%20to%20reporters%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20called%20up%20the%20Speaker%20last%20night%20in%20this%20connection.%20Speaker%20suggested%20meeting%20him%20the%20next%20day.%20As%20per%20his%20suggestion%2C%20when%20I%20called%20him%20up%20once%20again%20this%20morning%2C%20he%20told%20me%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20Secretary-General%20and%20submit%20the%20documents%20to%20his%20office.%20I%20called%20up%20the%20Secretary-General%20who%20said%20that%20his%20office%20is%20closed%20today%20and%20told%20me%20to%20submit%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%A6I%20sent%20the%20letter%20by%20post.%20They%20signed%20the%20letter%20but%20did%20not%20stamp%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20decision%20to%20reinstate%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RahulGandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20MP%20is%20a%20welcome%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20brings%20relief%20to%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20and%20especially%20to%20Wayanad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20time%20is%20left%20of%20their%20tenure%2C%20BJP%20and%20Modi%20Govt%20should%20utilise%20that%20by%20concentrating%20on%20actual%20governance%20rather%20than%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkikcZqfFvn%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FkikcZqfFvn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1688417638613938176%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20membership%20was%20restored%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20that%20it%20welcomed%20the%20development%20even%20though%20it%20was%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMohabbat%20ne%20nafrat%20ko%20hara%20diya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Love%20has%20defeated%20hate)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Gourav%20Vallabh%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVallabh%20added%20that%20the%20move%20was%20welcome%2C%20%E2%80%9Calthough%20it%20was%20not%20with%20the%20same%20speed%20as%20the%20disqualification%20after%20the%20Surat%20judgment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20Modi%20and%20Rahul%20will%20be%20in%20parliament%C2%A0%20together%20and%20be%20ready%20for%20questions%20in%20parliament%20on%20the%20Adani%20group%20and%20more%20importantly%20when%20Manipur%20was%20burning%20and%20is%20still%20burning%2C%20where%20was%20Modiji%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20answer%20you%20and%20you%20cannot%20run%20away%20from%20that%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20Gandhi%20will%20speak%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20scheduled%20for%20Tuesday%20and%20Wednesday%2C%20Vallabh%20said%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20committee%20will%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20yes%2C%20he%20is%20our%20senior%20leader%20and%20all%20Congress%20workers%20want%20that%20he%20should%20speak%20in%20parliament%20and%20raise%20questions%20like%20he%20used%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Vallabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defamation%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20Gandhi%20for%20his%20comments%20in%20Kolar%20before%20the%202019%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20filed%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Purnesh%20Modi%20who%20said%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20defamed%20the%20%E2%80%98Modi%20community%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20question.%20Why%20do%20all%20these%20thieves%20have%20Modi%20in%20their%20names%20whether%20it%20is%20Nirav%20Modi%2C%20Lalit%20Modi%20or%20Narendra%20Modi%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20many%20more%20such%20Modis%20will%20com