%20assisted%20more%20than%204%2C000%20migrant%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Vijay%20Kumar%20%3Cem%3E(name%20changed)%20%3C%2Fem%3Egot%20enrolled%20in%20Azim%20Premji%20University%20for%20a%20BA%20Honours%20(Economics)%20course%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Gubbachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2013%2C%20Vijay%20migrated%20from%20his%20home%20state%20Jharkhand%20for%20better%20schooling%20and%20to%20live%20with%20his%20father%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20house%20helper%20for%20a%20wealthy%20Bengaluru%20family.%20But%2C%20Vijay%20was%20denied%20admission%20to%20a%20local%20private%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20understand%20English%20and%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20other%20subjects%20like%20Maths.%20I%20left%20school%20after%20Class%205%2C%20so%20my%20basics%20were%20not%20clear.%20My%20Maths%20understanding%20was%20of%20Class%203%20level.%20So%20I%20was%20denied%20admission%20and%20I%20felt%20dejected%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20now%2018-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20learnt%20about%20Gubbachi%20from%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20employer.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20non-profit%E2%80%99s%20programme%2C%20where%20he%20was%20trained%20to%20read%20and%20write%20English%20and%20understand%20Mathematics.%20After%20a%20year%2C%20the%20organisation%20helped%20him%20enrol%20for%20senior%20secondary%20schooling%20(Class%2010)%20at%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS)%2C%20a%20government-run%20%E2%80%9Copen%20school%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20explained%20concepts%20to%20me%20in%20my%20language%20and%20helped%20me%20read%20textbooks.%20They%20emphasised%20that%20memorising%20exact%20vocabulary%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20necessary%2C%20and%20I%20always%20wrote%20down%20what%20I%20understood.%20This%20approach%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20grasp%20the%20subject