lass%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnd%20men%2C%20too%2C%20have%20been%20playing%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20Pali%20Hill%E2%80%99s%20transformation.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPHRA%20achieved%20a%20significant%20milestone%20when%20their%20garbage%20management%20led%20to%20producing%20energy%20from%20wet%20garbage.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20was%20a%20decade-long%20endeavour%2C%20starting%20with%20door-to-door%20garbage%20collection%2C%20where%20members%20worked%20towards%20creating%20awareness%20about%20segregation%2C%20overcoming%20initial%20resistance%2C%20and%20finally%20implementing%20it%20with%20BMC%E2%80%99s%20help.%20%E2%80%9CBy%202019%2C%20we%20were%20segragating%20almost%2090%25%20of%20our%20waste.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20garbage%20going%20to%20the%20dumping%20ground%20reduced%20from%202.2%20tons%20to%20800%20kg%20per%20day%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Madhu%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20with%20this%20segregated%20wet%20waste%20that%20PHRA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F215606%2Flpg-price-hike-how-to-set-up-biogas-plant-kitchen-fuel-apartment-complex-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eset%20up%20a%20biogas%20plant%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20collaboration%20with%20BMC%20on%20the%20Pali%20Hill%20Water%20Reservoir%20ground%20in%202018.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20plant%20converts%20one%20ton%20of%20wet%20waste%20daily%20into%20about%20160%20units%20of%20energy%2C%20which%20powers%20our%20street%20lights%2C%20as%20well%20runs%20the%20plant.%20It%20generated%20electricity%20worth%20Rs%208-10%20lakh%20at%20no%20cost%20to%20BMC%2C%20and%20saved%20an%20additional%20Rs%203%20lakh%20spent%20on%20garbage%20transportation.%20The%20residual%20compost%20is%20distributed%20for%20free%20among%20housing%20societies%20for%20community%20gardening%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20Madhu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPHRA%20rai